content.rendered:
Directed by B.V. Nandini Reddy

Written by Lakshmi Bhupala

Cast Samantha Ruth Prabhu (Swathi). Lakshmi (Savitri ‘Baby’). Rajendra Prasad (Chanti). Teja Sajja (Rocky). Naga Shaurya (Vikram). Urvashi (Sulochana). Rao Ramesh (Shekhar). Pragathi (Madhavi). Aishwariyaa Bhaskaran (Vikram’s mother (as Aishwarya)). Naga Chaitanya Akkineni (Young Chanti) . Jagapathi Babu (God). Aneesha Dama (Divya). Element (Judge / footballer).R.J. Hemant. Sunny Mungara (Bicycle Owner). Praveen Navakoti (Event Organizer). Raja Ravindra (Inspector Sharma). B.V. Nandini Reddy ((as Nandini Reddy)). Adivi Sesh (Savitri’s husband). Snigdha (Jahnavi). Sunayana (Chanti’s daughter)

Languages Telugu

Producers D. Suresh Babu. Vamsi Bandaru. Vijay Shankar Donkada. Yuvraj Karthikeyan. Hyunwoo Thomas Kim. Sujith Kumar Kolli. Vivek Kuchibhotla. T.G. Vishwa Prasad. Sunitha Tati. Divya Vijay

Production Suresh Production. People Media Factor. Guru Film.
